College Nine/John R. Lewis Dining Hall.name: College Nine/John R. Lewis Dining Hall
College Nine/John R. Lewis Dining Hall.description: Nestled in the redwoods near the academic campus core, this is our largest dining hall. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted.

Cowell/Stevenson Dining Hall.name: Cowell/Stevenson Dining Hall
Cowell/Stevenson Dining Hall.description: Located on the hill above the East Field, this dining hall features a fantastic view of the Monterey Bay, with outdoor patio dining available to capture the crisp ocean breezes. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted.

Crown/Merrill Dining Hall.name: Crown/Merrill Dining Hall
Crown/Merrill Dining Hall.description: Serving the east side of campus, this dining hall boasts a 20-foot salad bar. This is also the home of our campus bakery team, supplying fresh-baked goods to all our locations. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted.

Porter/Kresge Dining Hall.name: Porter/Kresge Dining Hall
Porter/Kresge Dining Hall.description: Serving the west side of campus, this dining hall features a remodeled serving area made with natural, sustainable textures and surfaces. Come enjoy the patio, perched high on the hill overlooking the bay. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted.

Rachel Carson/Oakes Dining Hall.name: Rachel Carson/Oakes Dining Hall
Rachel Carson/Oakes Dining Hall.description: Beautifully renovated dining hall with amazing views. This is the place to go for late night (Sunday–Thursday) and weekend dining on the west side of campus. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted.

Oakes Cafe.name: Oakes Cafe
Oakes Cafe.description: Located at Oakes College, Oakes Cafe offers breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

Global Village Cafe.name: Global Village Cafe
Global Village Cafe.description: Located in the McHenry Library lobby. Fuel your study session with one of our many delicious menu items and our selection of 100% organic coffee and teas. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

Slug Stop.name: Slug Stop
Slug Stop.description: Slug Stop market, located in Quarry Plaza, stocks a wide inventory of coffees & teas, sandwiches, salads, drinks, snacks, pastries, and convenience items. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

Stevenson Coffee House.name: Stevenson Coffee House
Stevenson Coffee House.description: Established in 1975 and located at Stevenson College. This long-standing favorite offers espresso drinks, salads, sandwiches, their famous fudgies, and more. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

Porter Market.name: Porter Market
Porter Market.description: Located next to the Porter/Kresge Dining Hall, Porter Market offers grab-n-go meals, snacks, bottled beverages, smoothies, organic espresso drinks made-to-order, plus grocery and convenience items. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

Merrill Market.name: Merrill Market
Merrill Market.description: Located on the Merrill College plaza, Merrill Market offers grab-n-go meals, snacks, bottled beverages, smoothies, and organic coffee, plus grocery and convenience items. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, SNAP EBT, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$. Managed by UCSC Dining

University Center Cafe.name: UCen Coffee Bar
University Center Cafe.description: Located upstairs above College Nine/John R. Lewis Dining Hall, this cafe has grab-n-go meals, snacks, bottled beverages, smoothies, and organic espresso drinks made-to-order. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

Banana Joe's Late Night.name: Banana Joe's Late Night
Banana Joe's Late Night.description: Located at Crown College, this late night cafe offers student favorites like burgers, fries, and pizza. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

Perk Coffee Bar at Baskin Engineering.name: Perk Coffee Bars
Perk Coffee Bar at Baskin Engineering.description: Perk Coffee Bars offer 100% organic coffee and a wide selection of freshly baked muffins, Bagelry bagels, and pastries. Stop by for a latte or mocha, or meet friends for a quick lunch from the selection of salads, sandwiches, and more. This Perk Coffee Bar can be found in the lobby of Baskin Engineering. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

University Center Bistro.description: University Center Bistro offers upscale casual lunchtime dining with friendly servers and an incredible menu. Were located above the College Nine/John R. Lewis Dining Hall. Slug Points, Banana Bucks, Flexi Dollars, and credit cards accepted. Get 10% off when you pay with Slug Points, Banana Bucks, or Flexi$.

Iv\u00e9ta Cafe.name: Ivéta Cafe
Iv\u00e9ta Cafe.description: Serving breakfast, lunch and dinner, with options such as organic egg dishes, fresh salads, gourmet sandwiches, and much more. Credit cards and Flexi Dollars accepted. Online ordering available. ✉ cafe@iveta.com
